            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Ok, I understand about not encouraging bad practices. I\u2019ll add update_wrapper as appropriate if you want to merge this patch in spite of that. Admittedly, the use case is small.\n\nFor reference, here is the Markdown filter without this patch in Flask:\n\n``` python\nfrom flask import Flask, Markup\nfrom markdown import markdown\n\n@app.template_filter(name='markdown')\ndef markdown_filter(text, *args, **kwargs):\n    # Customize arguments here\n    return Markup(markdown(text, *args, **kwargs))\n```\n"
